{"snp1.10:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.10 ","snp1.10:0.2":"Alavakasutta ","snp1.10:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp1.10:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava alaviyam viharati alavakassa yakkhassa bhavane. ","snp1.10:1.3":"Atha kho alavako yakkho yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp1.10:1.4":"“nikkhama, samana”ti. ","snp1.10:1.5":"“Sadhavuso”ti bhagava nikkhami. ","snp1.10:1.6":"“Pavisa, samana”ti. ","snp1.10:1.7":"“Sadhavuso”ti bhagava pavisi. ","snp1.10:2.1":"Dutiyampi kho …pe… ","snp1.10:2.2":"tatiyampi kho alavako yakkho bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp1.10:2.3":"“nikkhama, samana”ti. ","snp1.10:2.4":"“Sadhavuso”ti bhagava nikkhami. ","snp1.10:2.5":"“Pavisa, samana”ti. ","snp1.10:2.6":"“Sadhavuso”ti bhagava pavisi. ","snp1.10:3.1":"Catutthampi kho alavako yakkho bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp1.10:3.2":"“nikkhama, samana”ti. ","snp1.10:3.3":"“Na khvaham tam, avuso, nikkhamissami. ","snp1.10:3.4":"Yam te karaniyam, tam karohi”ti. ","snp1.10:4.1":"“Panham tam, samana, pucchissami. ","snp1.10:4.2":"Sace me na byakarissasi, cittam va te khipissami, hadayam va te phalessami, padesu va gahetva paragangaya khipissami”ti. ","snp1.10:5.1":"“Na khvaham tam, avuso, passami sadevake loke samarake sabrahmake sassamanabrahmaniya pajaya sadevamanussaya yo me cittam va khipeyya hadayam va phaleyya padesu va gahetva paragangaya khipeyya. ","snp1.10:5.2":"Api ca tvam, avuso, puccha yadakankhasi”ti. ","snp1.10:5.3":"Atha kho alavako yakkho bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","snp1.10:6.1":"“Kim sudha vittam purisassa settham, ","snp1.10:6.2":"Kim su sucinnam sukhamavahati; ","snp1.10:6.3":"Kim su have sadutaram rasanam, ","snp1.10:6.4":"Kathamjivim jivitamahu settham”. ","snp1.10:7.1":"“Saddhidha vittam purisassa settham, ","snp1.10:7.2":"Dhammo sucinno sukhamavahati; ","snp1.10:7.3":"Saccam have sadutaram rasanam, ","snp1.10:7.4":"Pannajivim jivitamahu settham”. ","snp1.10:8.1":"“Katham su tarati ogham, ","snp1.10:8.2":"katham su tarati annavam; ","snp1.10:8.3":"Katham su dukkhamacceti, ","snp1.10:8.4":"katham su parisujjhati”. ","snp1.10:9.1":"“Saddhaya tarati ogham, ","snp1.10:9.2":"appamadena annavam; ","snp1.10:9.3":"Viriyena dukkhamacceti, ","snp1.10:9.4":"pannaya parisujjhati”. ","snp1.10:10.1":"“Katham su labhate pannam, ","snp1.10:10.2":"katham su vindate dhanam; ","snp1.10:10.3":"Katham su kittim pappoti, ","snp1.10:10.4":"katham mittani ganthati; ","snp1.10:10.5":"Asma loka param lokam, ","snp1.10:10.6":"katham pecca na socati”. ","snp1.10:11.1":"“Saddahano arahatam, ","snp1.10:11.2":"dhammam nibbanapattiya; ","snp1.10:11.3":"Sussusam labhate pannam, ","snp1.10:11.4":"appamatto vicakkhano. ","snp1.10:12.1":"Patirupakari dhurava, ","snp1.10:12.2":"utthata vindate dhanam; ","snp1.10:12.3":"Saccena kittim pappoti, ","snp1.10:12.4":"dadam mittani ganthati. ","snp1.10:13.1":"Yassete caturo dhamma, ","snp1.10:13.2":"saddhassa gharamesino; ","snp1.10:13.3":"Saccam dhammo dhiti cago, ","snp1.10:13.4":"sa ve pecca na socati. ","snp1.10:14.1":"Ingha annepi pucchassu, ","snp1.10:14.2":"puthu samanabrahmane; ","snp1.10:14.3":"Yadi sacca dama caga, ","snp1.10:14.4":"khantya bhiyyodha vijjati”. ","snp1.10:15.1":"“Katham nu dani puccheyyam, ","snp1.10:15.2":"Puthu samanabrahmane; ","snp1.10:15.3":"Yoham ajja pajanami, ","snp1.10:15.4":"Yo attho samparayiko. ","snp1.10:16.1":"Atthaya vata me buddho, ","snp1.10:16.2":"Vasayalavimagama; ","snp1.10:16.3":"Yoham ajja pajanami, ","snp1.10:16.4":"Yattha dinnam mahapphalam. ","snp1.10:17.1":"So aham vicarissami, ","snp1.10:17.2":"Gama gamam pura puram; ","snp1.10:17.3":"Namassamano sambuddham, ","snp1.10:17.4":"Dhammassa ca sudhammatan”ti. ","snp1.10:17.5":"Alavakasuttam dasamam. "}